citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 3:13pm on
September 27, 2023.
Upon arrival, the inspector made contact with the licensee by phone, stating no one would be available for an inspection
before later that evening.
End Section
